title: [The 1958 Hickory Miss Australia Quest]
brief_description: A record of the 1958 Miss Australia quest. The following women represent their state: Pamela McKAy (QLD); Lois Johnson (ACT); Judith Carton (NSW); Thelma Wright (Vic); Jennifer Flower (SA); Judith Deal (Tas); Carmel Klune (WA). 1957 Miss Australia Helen Wood appears on the judging panel.
